        <article>
          <h3>1. What is The Bored Dinosaur NFT Marketplace?</h3>
            <p>
                The Bored Dinosaur NFT Marketplace is your go-to destination for rare, 
                curated dinosaur-themed NFTs. Each token represents a unique, digital 
                collectible stored securely on the blockchain.
            </p>
        </article>
      
        <article>
          <h3>2. How do I purchase an NFT?</h3>
            <p>
                Simply browse our homepage, add your favorite dinosaur NFTs to your 
                cart, and proceed to checkout. Once your payment is confirmed, we’ll 
                provide you with a unique key to add the NFT to your digital wallet.          
            </p>
        </article>
      
        <article>
          <h3>3. Why are these NFTs special?</h3>
            <p>
                Our NFTs are one-of-a-kind and available in limited quantities, 
                making them perfect for collectors. Each design is inspired by the 
                fascinating world of dinosaurs and brought to life using blockchain 
                technology.
            </p>
        </article>

        <article>
            <h3>4. What do I need to get started?</h3>
              <p>
                To purchase and store NFTs, you’ll need a digital wallet like 
                MetaMask or Trust Wallet. If you don’t have one yet, setting it up is quick and easy.
              </p>
        </article>

        <article>
            <h3>5. What blockchain does this platform use?</h3>
              <p>
                Our NFTs are minted on Ethereum, ensuring transparency, security, 
                and compatibility with major marketplaces.
              </p>
        </article>

        <article>
            <h3>6. Can I trade or resell my NFTs?</h3>
              <p>
                Yes! You own the NFT once you’ve purchased it. You can 
                resell or trade it on compatible marketplaces like OpenSea at your discretion.
              </p>
        </article>

        <article>
            <h3>7. What happens if I lose my unique key?</h3>
              <p>
                Unfortunately, for security reasons, we cannot recover lost keys. Please 
                store your keys in a secure place to ensure access to your NFTs.
              </p>
        </article>

        <article>
            <h3>8. How can I contact support?</h3>
