                For any questions or assistance, feel free to email us at 
                <a href="mailto:support@boreddinosaurnft.com">support@boreddinosaurnft.com</a>
                or reach out through the contact form on our website.
              </p>
        </article>

        <article>
            <h3>9. Can I buy a dinosaur NFT with pizza?</h3>
              <p>
                Unfortunately, as cool as it would be to trade pizza for NFTs, 
                we can only accept traditional payment methods like credit cards or 
                crypto. But hey, keep an eye on our future updates—who knows what we might accept next?
              </p>
        </article>

        <article>
            <h3>10. What happens if I accidentally buy a dinosaur that isn’t as rare as I thought?</h3>
              <p>
                Don’t worry! All of our dinosaurs are rare in their own way, and each one 
                comes with its own unique charm. But if you want a truly one-of-a-kind 
                dinosaur, check out our limited edition collection—those babies are the rarest of them all!
              </p>
        </article>

